~z~Okay then Alex, I'll come and get you in the next hour.

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~心理医生说以我现在的情绪状态最好不要见任何人，改天再联系我吧...

~z~There are plenty of guys who'd kill to collect me from the hospital. I'll call one of them.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~有的是人愿意来医院接我，我找他们了。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我现在不能陪你。还得好好陪着我亲爹，否则就没人帮我付信用卡账单了。

GCA_ACT_CALL_VERYIRATE
GCA_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_YES

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，我刚准备的差不多，但也没事。

GCA_ACT_GETCALL_REJECT_VERYIRATE
~z~I'm sorry but I've got to see the girls. Maybe another time.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~很抱歉，但我跟姐妹们有约在先。下次再说吧。

GCA_ACT_CALL_LIKENO_2_AA

~z~I'm not saying this is over for good but I need a break.

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，为了跟你约会我推了很多人，不过...好吧。

~z~This is a fucking joke. You never want to go out with me.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~这他妈就是开玩笑。你根本不想和我出去玩。

~z~Oh, you picked up. I was starting to think I'd have to get Daddy's private investigator to track you down, Niko.

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Are you fucking stupid? I'm sleeping. Call me back after noon. I might be awake then.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~你他妈白痴吧？我正睡觉呢。下午再找我，那会儿我可能醒着。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I would have been better off putting my energy into a block of wood than you.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，把心思花在木头上都比花在你身上强。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Alex, that you?

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我现在不能带你出去，Alex。晚点我再打给你。

GCA_ACT_CALL_LIKENO_1_AB

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Niko，其实我比较希望我的约会对象能好看点，这样被狗仔队拍到也不会太尴尬。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~I am a beautiful flower and I need to be treated with care. And if you do that, I might date you again.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我是一枝美丽的鲜花，需要精心照顾。你能做到的话，也许还有约会的机会。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, Niko. But my friends just saw us out again and they might actually think we were serious. Leave it a bit.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，Niko。但朋友刚看见我俩一起出去过，她们可能以为我俩真的在交往了。过几天再说吧。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Okay, pick me up in the next hour and you can take me out.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好的，一小时内来接我，带我出去玩。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Alex，我想去买点衣服。你能给我点优惠吗？

GCA_ACT_PAL_GETCALL_HOSP_NO

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~当然了，Niko。我跟店里的人打声招呼，你今天就能拿到优惠价了。

~z~Niko, I am not someone you want to fuck things up with. You will regret losing me for the rest of your life.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我不是可以随便糊弄的人。失去我你会后悔终身的。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~心理医生没说错，他对你的评价完全正确。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Do you want to take me out?
~z~I'm scared that if we see each other this much someone's going to get hurt. In a while, maybe.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我担心咱俩见面这么频繁，会有人受伤的。还是过段时间吧。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Okay Niko, we can go on a date. Come pick me up in the next hour.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好的，Niko，我们去约会吧。一小时内来接我。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我这样的女孩不该被你这种人这般对待。你好好考虑下，Niko。

GCA_ACT_CALL_DATE_YES

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好的，我去安排一下。今天一天你都可以在自由城的大商场拿到五折优惠。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~See you soon, Alex.
~z~So you're still on the scene, are you?

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我不想让咱俩走得太近。还是不要这么频繁地见面了。改天再说吧。

GCA1AUD.original: GCA_ACT_GETCALL_DATE
~z~Shit, I would have been better off putting my energy into a block of wood than you.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，把心思花在木头上都比花在你身上强。

~z~Sorry, Alex, but I kind of have a lot on my plate. But maybe another time.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，Alex，但我现在有点忙。改天再见吧。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~谈恋爱不是走独木桥，Niko。没有你来我往可是会失去我的。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~I'll go on a date with you, Niko. Pick me up in the next hour.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我愿意和你约会，Niko。一小时内来接我吧。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好消息，Alex。你不用担心跟着我会受苦了，咱俩到头了。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~包在我身上，Niko。你今天全天都有五折优惠。一定要买件好衣服啊。

GCA_ACT_PAL_CALL_HILIKE

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~要不是情况紧急，我也不会来麻烦你。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，Alex，但我突然有急事，不能来医院接你了。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~I'll give you another chance, Niko. But this better be the best date of my life though. Come collect me in an hour.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我再给你一次机会，Niko。但这最好是我这辈子最棒的约会。一小时内来接我吧。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~My therapist was right. He was totally right about you.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~心理医生没说错，他对你的评价完全正确。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Alex here, Niko.
~z~Fine, Niko. I'll call a cab.
~z~Niko, time to earn some brownie points. Would you pick me up from the hospital?
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，是时候挣点印象分了。你愿意来医院接我吗？

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~A woman has needs, Niko. If you aren't prepared to meet those needs then she might look elsewhere.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~女人也有需求，Niko。如果你满足不了需求，她可能会去找其他人。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~I'd like to see you.
GCA_ACT_CALL_LIKENO_1_AA
~z~That's fine, Niko. I'll just meet up with the girls.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~那好吧，Niko。我和姐妹们出去玩好了。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Well I'll get someone else to do it, goodbye.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~那我就找其他人来接我了，再见。

GCA1AUD.original: GCA_ACT_GETCALL_GREET
~z~I'd like to buy some stuff. Can you arrange a discount for me?
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~我想去买点东西。你能安排我一些折扣吗？

~z~From now on I am only dating Americans.
~z~Sure, I'll let you take me out. Come pick me up in the next hour.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~好啊，带我出去玩吧。一小时内过来接我。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Sorry Alex. I got more important things to be doing.
~z~Alright, Niko. Treat me like this then.
~z~Okay, I'll come and pick you up in the next hour.
~z~I feel like you should take me out on a date.
GCA_ACT_GETCALL_REJECT_IRATE
GCA_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_NO
GCA_CBRKUP
~z~There's mysterious and then there's a little too fucking mysterious Mr. European.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~在神秘的一天遇上了更神秘的欧洲猛男。

GCA1AUD.original: ~z~Niko, I am an intellectual, beautiful, and interesting woman. I do not need to see a man who treats me like you do.
GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我是一个聪明美丽又有趣的女人。没必要和一个像你这样对我的男人见面。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，Niko。现在不行。如果你给我更多的关注，我可能会帮你。

GCA1AUD.translated: ~z~Alex，你可是个社交名媛。总有其他认识的人能来接你吧。

GCA1AUD.original: GCA_ACT_PAL_CALL_GREET
~z~I'm not used to taking rejection, Niko. Goodbye.
~z~You want to go on a date?
~z~Sure, wait for me.
